{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"History.go()","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/go","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History_API\">History API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration\"><code>scrollRestoration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/state\"><code>state</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/back\"><code>back()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/forward\"><code>forward()</code></a></li><li><em><code>go()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/pushState\"><code>pushState()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/replaceState\"><code>replaceState()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>History.go()</code></strong> 메서드는 history 세션에서 특정한 페이지를 로딩합니다. 인자로 전달하는 파라미터 값에 따라 history를 통해서 페이지를 앞 뒤로 이동할 수 있습니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>이 메서드는&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Asynchronous\">asynchronous <small>(en-US)</small></a>(비동기)로 동작합니다. 페이지 앞, 뒤 이동이 언제 이뤄지는지 알려면&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\" title=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/popstate\">popstate</a></code> event에 대한 listener를 등록합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"구문","title":"구문","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">history.go([<em>delta</em>])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"delta\"><code>delta</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>현재 페이지에서 상대적으로 이동하려고 하는 history의 위치 값. 음수 값은 뒤로 이동하고, 양수 값은 앞으로 이동합니다. 예를 들면&nbsp;<code>history.go(2)</code>&nbsp;는 현재 페이지에서 2 페이지 앞으로 이동하고, <code>history.go(-2)</code>&nbsp;는 현재 페이지에서 2 페이지 뒤로 이동합니다. 만약 값을 전달하지 않거나, <code>delta</code>&nbsp;값을 0으로 전달한다면, 이는&nbsp;<code>location.reload()</code>를 동작시켰을 때와 동일한 결과를 보입니다. (새로고침)</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<p>한 페이지 뒤로 가기 (<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/back\" title=\"back()\"><code>back()</code></a>를 호출한 것과 동일):</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js line-numbers language-js notranslate\"><code>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/forward\" title=\"forward()\"><code>forward()</code></a>와 동일한 한 페이지 앞으로 가기:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js line-numbers language-js notranslate\"><code>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>두 페이지 앞으로 가기:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>두 페이지 뒤로 가기:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>마지막으로, 아래 구문들은 현재 페이지를 새로고침 합니다:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/history.html#dom-history-go\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'History.go()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No change from <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML5' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/browsers.html#dom-history-go\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'History.go()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"api.History.go","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/go/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/back\" title=\"back()\"><code>back()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/forward\" title=\"forward()\"><code>forward()</code></a></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\" title=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/popstate\">popstate</a></code> event</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History_API/Working_with_the_History_API\">Working with the History API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"구문","id":"구문"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"History.go() 메서드는 history 세션에서 특정한 페이지를 로딩합니다. 인자로 전달하는 파라미터 값에 따라 history를 통해서 페이지를 앞 뒤로 이동할 수 있습니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"History.go()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"History.go()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"History.go()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"go()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/history/go","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/history/go/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History","title":"History"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/go","title":"History.go()"}],"pageTitle":"History.go() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}